00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.500
5 Types of Depressive Disorders

00:00:11.450 --> 00:00:13.259
Depression is a very misunderstood disorder

00:00:14.110 --> 00:00:19.829
People will tend to stereotype depression and make it seem as though you are typically sad all the time and hate the world

00:00:19.960 --> 00:00:21.960
But that is far from the truth

00:00:23.020 --> 00:00:29.429
Depression has sub disorders that will have different symptoms intensities and causes here are the different types of depression

00:00:31.180 --> 00:00:33.780
Disruptive Mood Dysregulation Disorder

00:00:33.780 --> 00:00:40.160
If you tend to have continuous outbursts of temper either physical or verbal and it happens three times a week

00:00:40.420 --> 00:00:44.480
That is one of the symptoms for Disruptive Mood Dysregulation Disorder

00:00:44.740 --> 00:00:51.000
Other symptoms that you could experience are feeling sad or moody besides the anger three times a week or

00:00:51.369 --> 00:00:55.559
having severe outbursts. It's more likely that you have this disorder

00:00:55.559 --> 00:01:00.628
if these symptoms have occurred for more than a year, or if the symptoms started before the age of 10

00:01:01.989 --> 00:01:07.829
Another sub disorder of depression is major depressive disorder which can also be known as clinical depression

00:01:08.500 --> 00:01:15.300
Those with this disorder may have an episode for longer periods of time while others may only have had an episode once in their life

00:01:16.060 --> 00:01:21.900
People with MDD have the following symptoms for nearly a two-week span and it will usually arise everyday

00:01:22.930 --> 00:01:25.319
Feeling hopeless sad or numb;

00:01:26.350 --> 00:01:28.860
Decreased motivation for things that they used to like;

00:01:29.980 --> 00:01:34.559
Increased or decreased appetite which could lead to weight gain or loss respectively;

00:01:35.290 --> 00:01:39.150
Changes in sleep; Fatigue; Being unable to concentrate;

00:01:40.060 --> 00:01:42.839
Forgetfulness; Thoughts of death or suicide;

00:01:43.600 --> 00:01:46.050
Suicide attempts and self-harm.

00:01:47.260 --> 00:01:50.039
MDD can be mixed with different disorders like anxiety;

00:01:50.950 --> 00:01:57.150
melancholic features; catatonia; peripartum onset; psychotic features and seasonal patterns.

00:01:58.180 --> 00:02:02.129
Persistent depressive disorder also known as dysthymia is an ongoing

00:02:02.530 --> 00:02:06.089
depressive disorder the symptoms are not as clear as MDD,

00:02:06.100 --> 00:02:13.080
however the symptoms usually happen almost every day for two years in adults, and at least one year for children and adolescents

00:02:13.610 --> 00:02:21.580
The symptoms that go along with dysthymia are appetite change; change in sleep cycle; low energy; poor self-esteem;

00:02:22.250 --> 00:02:27.309
feelings of hopelessness; bad concentration; forgetfulness and lack of motivation

00:02:28.400 --> 00:02:34.000
Dysthymia can be mixed with other disorders just like MDD; it can also range in levels of severity

00:02:35.629 --> 00:02:41.739
Premenstrual dysphoric disorder is disabling approximately three to eight percent of women and no one can really figure out why

00:02:42.170 --> 00:02:49.089
The following symptoms occur during the menstrual cycle and a usual diagnosis would require at least five of the following symptoms to be present

00:02:49.640 --> 00:02:51.049
mood swings;

00:02:51.049 --> 00:02:52.670
increased sensitivity;

00:02:52.670 --> 00:02:55.089
feelings of hopelessness or being overwhelmed;

00:02:56.060 --> 00:03:03.579
anxiety; feeling tired and sluggish; a lack of interest in activities and insomnia or excessive amounts of sleep

00:03:04.040 --> 00:03:11.739
The disorder also has physical symptoms such as joint pain; bloating; weight gain; tender breasts and swelling

00:03:12.319 --> 00:03:16.119
This disorder will affect school, work and relationships

00:03:17.660 --> 00:03:24.249
Substance/medication induced depressive disorder. This disorder is present during the use of medication or during substance abuse

00:03:24.769 --> 00:03:26.769
Symptoms include irritability;

00:03:27.319 --> 00:03:33.458
Depressive episodes; bad temper; the sense of hopelessness and no interest or pleasure in anything

00:03:33.980 --> 00:03:39.459
These symptoms will occur when using the substance or win in withdrawal. Most people use drugs

00:03:39.459 --> 00:03:45.789
Or substances to feel better and will usually not notice the symptoms. They have for substance medication and use depressive disorder

00:03:47.720 --> 00:03:51.160
Depressive disorder due to another medical condition is another type of depression

00:03:52.160 --> 00:03:54.160
arthritis diabetes HIV

00:03:54.919 --> 00:03:58.719
Strokes viral infections and much more can cause you to have depression

00:03:59.389 --> 00:04:06.519
symptoms can include a persistent depressive mood lack of interest irritability and an elevated or expansive mood

00:04:07.190 --> 00:04:10.929
We hope this helps you out if you experience any of these symptoms

00:04:11.419 --> 00:04:16.749
Please see your doctor or find someone you trust to talk to especially if your symptoms persist

